{"tid":2110076,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"政府就公務員宣誓效忠特區展開諮詢","createTime":"2020-07-15T15:34:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-16T05:05:37.000Z","uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d9fbf003c09bbf066f271d960b487f179663ffbe","tid":2110076,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T15:34:53.000Z","msg":"公務員事務局局長聶德權去信公務員，就有關公務員宣誓擁護基本法及效忠香港特區政府的政策諮詢公務員意見。<br />\n<br />\n聶德權發信給全體公務員，提到近日建議新入職公務員、現職公務員升職或轉職等，需簽署文件或宣誓擁護基本法及效忠香港特區。<br />\n<br />\n他表示，知道有公務員可能關注誓詞及聲明內容違反要求會有甚麼後果、何時把要求擴展至所有公務員等，他指落實建議時，必定小心全面考慮，包括如公務員未有遵從要求或違反誓言時，應採取的跟進行動及相關機制。<br />\n<br />\n他重申，擁護基本法及效忠香港特區是公務員一貫責任，亦是市民期望。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=398100\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D398100&d=CgM6%2BPDcwTI4Uk%2BisK9n3yfe5Xzx4ME6JwL9AZsFK0I%3D&h=d674d4b7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D398100&h=1c7dd0a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=398100</a>"},{"pid":"1392d4452edf2b9f1c8d9a7d6e1d88af6e6e1ad0","tid":2110076,"uid":258731,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T15:38:55.000Z","msg":"5毛pr: 繼續批鬥公務員<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddb33abe1d4482ccf63b83acc1cc4100a49c1750","tid":2110076,"uid":85629,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T00:46:26.000Z","msg":"呢啲都會諮詢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d4da2141efab178f7825a49874851566b79a7e0","tid":2110076,"uid":111153,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T00:48:47.000Z","msg":"假諮詢 反對者送中究治 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b36c8437995253ce84d6c7e1b6cc73ee3f06d2b1","tid":2110076,"uid":301923,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T05:05:37.